{"tid":1278361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次7.1嘅行動，其實算成功，大家唔好灰心，要繼續撐住！","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T18:32:44.000Z","uid":210794,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd7e05554e6e4e2f1b4f32f9d14ef4a37998ba8e","tid":1278361,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:14:18.000Z","msg":"（利申唔係階段性勝利）<br />\n<br />\n夜晚攻佔立法會當然唔使講啦⋯⋯<br />\n但原定朝早嘅不舉行動雖然攻唔入金紫荊，水馬都未掂到，但喺龍匯龍和守防線（以及我哋俾狗打）都畀到班狗官壓力，嚇到佢哋要入室內睇扯旗！<br />\n當然我哋下晝仲成功扯低支那旗！<br />\n<br />\n所以大家千祈唔好灰！雖然成場war未贏，但7.1呢個Battle係算成功！（當然有兄弟被捕，呢啲一定唔可以忘記，一定要救！）<br />\n<br />\n不撤不散！Free Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"25c92a7f3803684e88b25ecdcd01c74daa5fb689","tid":1278361,"uid":81150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"登記做選民<br />\n最後今晚!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a>"},{"pid":"51526478d412a5fa3a786dab674f2ea7cb11eb8e","tid":1278361,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25c92a7f3803684e88b25ecdcd01c74daa5fb689","tid":1278361,"uid":81150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"登記做選民<br />\n最後今晚!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"一早已經係，<br />\n可惜我喺外國讀書，十一月唔會喺香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5834d31785709649a0b7294ddf1c7a1c99ca1e6a","tid":1278361,"uid":268431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"其實呢次 好撚成功，最高權力中心，停止運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi